name: Anatomical and neuronal distribution of the G-coupled protein receptor 75 mRNA in the mouse central nervous system
citation: Gamboa, Alec (2025) Anatomical and neuronal distribution of the G-coupled protein receptor 75 mRNA in the mouse central nervous system (Version draft) [Data set]. DANDI Archive. https://dandiarchive.org/dandiset/001639/draft
description: Fluorescent in situ hybridization performed alongside immunohistochemistry to allow for characterization and co-localization analysis of g-protein coupled receptor 75 (GPR75) with different neuronal subtypes. Behavioral experiments were also conducted to further characterize GPR75.
